<view class="page paper-page kingdom-page">
  <view class="page-head kingdom-head paper-title kingdom-title-board">
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--red"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--green"></view>
    <view class="paper-corner bottom-left"></view>
    <view class="paper-corner bottom-right"></view>
    <text class="paper-title__stamp">吗喽王国地图</text>
    <text class="hero-title">{{appMeta.appName}}</text>
    <text class="subtext">{{appMeta.slogan}}</text>
    <view class="kingdom-title-markers">
      <text>记录处</text><text>复盘台</text><text>计划屋</text>
    </view>
    <view class="paper-title__rail">
      <view class="paper-title__rail-line"></view>
      <view class="paper-title__rail-dot"></view>
      <view class="paper-title__rail-dot"></view>
      <view class="paper-title__rail-line"></view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="amulet-card amulet-frame status-card {{croissant.statusClass}} kingdom-status">
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-right corner-ornament--gold"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-bottom-left corner-ornament--green"></view>
    <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-bottom-right corner-ornament--red"></view>
    <text class="amulet-frame__seal">Croissant 护身符</text>
    <text class="status-name">{{croissant.status}}</text>
    <text class="status-wear">磨损值：{{croissant.wear}}</text>
    <text class="body-text">{{croissant.explanation}}</text>
    <view class="ornament-line amulet-frame__bottom"></view>
    <text class="protect-note">{{croissant.advice}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="note-card welcome-card paper-edge">
    <view class="paper-corner right"></view>
    <text>欢迎回到吗喽王国。</text>
    <text>今天也不用立刻做决定。</text>
    <text>先看看 Croissant 现在需要什么。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="map-shell">
    <view class="floral-divider">
      <view class="floral-divider__line"></view>
      <view class="floral-divider__dot blue"></view>
      <view class="floral-divider__dot gold"></view>
      <view class="floral-divider__line"></view>
    </view>
    <text class="ribbon-title">王国地点</text>
    <view class="map-trail">
      <block wx:for="{{navItems}}" wx:key="path">
        <view class="map-stop {{index % 2 === 0 ? 'left' : 'right'}}">
          <view class="map-route-pin"><text>{{index + 1}}</text></view>
          <view class="map-place map-card {{item.color}} {{item.size}}" data-path="{{item.path}}" bindtap="goTo">
            <view class="corner-ornament corner-ornament-left corner-ornament--gold"></view>
            <view class="paper-corner bottom-right"></view>
            <text class="map-place__seal">{{item.alias}}</text>
            <text class="map-place__title">{{item.label}}</text>
            <text class="map-place__desc">{{item.subtitle}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
        <view wx:if="{{index < navItems.length - 1}}" class="map-route"></view>
      </block>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="floral-divider bottom-divider">
    <view class="floral-divider__line"></view>
    <view class="floral-divider__dot red"></view>
    <view class="floral-divider__dot gold"></view>
    <view class="floral-divider__dot green"></view>
    <view class="floral-divider__line"></view>
  </view>
  <text class="version-note">当前版本：{{appMeta.version}} {{appMeta.stage}}</text>
</view>